{
  "stem": "24554.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, why you don't go to the Czechoslovak army, you can go in the Russian army, I said, I am not a Russian.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You told me I am without citizenship, when you took me in the army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this to allowed me to go in the army, I'd need 10 months to give me permission to go to the army.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was from Dushanbe, yes, Stalinabad, to Buzuluk, under the Uran.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To come to the army, it needs nearly three weeks in train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was more or less a normal train, normal carriages, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, it wasn't so difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First of all, they give us some eat, you know, to take with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had money-- you know, what I sell my shirt, shoes and watch.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I wasn't short in money, luckily.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I come to Buzuluk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, some Czechoslovak boys, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember their names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Around five-- I don't remember, exactly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I come to Buzuluk, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first thing, when I was the army, they cut the hair.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are full of-- how you call?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, these small these louses, so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they cut the hair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was wintertime, spring-- it was too cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I take my this on the head, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was in Buzuluk, I must make all their [INAUDIBLE] these-- so they give me back my [INAUDIBLE] this In 19-- They knew you were a sergeant?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I must make exams, and witnesses, and this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Buzuluk, in the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They take us for-- not only me-- for six weeks exercise, and like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So after six weeks, they give me back my-- [TAPS SHOULDER] this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, in Buzuluk, it was more or less [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
